          </div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The present invention relates to one kind of method for detecting link state in multiple service transmitting platform. The method is to count frame number of frames in virtual container in set period and one method of judging link state near the service layer without increase in the transmission bandwidth and obvious increase of CPU load. The present invention maintains the accessibility of the link and can avoid long time link jamming causing network collapse.</td> 
